Basic Manipulation
========================================================

- `git init`
- `git clone`
- `git add`
- `git commit`
- `git pull`
- `git push`

**Note**: Keep your stage area clean.

Undo
========================================================

- `git checkout -- filename`
- `git reset HEAD filename`
- `git reset --hard log_id`

Branch
========================================================

- `git checkout -b bname`
- `git branch` and `git checkout bname`

Merge
========================================================

- whole branch. `git merge --no-ff -m "comments" feature_branch`
- specific file or direcotry. `git checkout feature_branch -- blabla/blabla` and `git commit -m "comments"`


Configuration
=========================================================

- `git config --global core.autocrlf false`
- `git config --global core.safecrlf true`

Keep synchronous with remote dev branch
=========================================================

- `git checkout -b branch_name origin/branch_name`
